{"tid":2024840,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[撐港台嘅同我入嚟] 侮辱警察? 邊度辱呀? 睇過?","createTime":"2020-05-20T01:02:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-20T02:41:47.000Z","uid":184643,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4ff235e3ba8057b8cc605dd2b716fb761b00fc42","tid":2024840,"uid":184643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T01:02:40.000Z","msg":"＝＝＝＝＝＝行動＝＝＝＝＝＝<br />\nDOs：<br />\n1）星期五睇頭條直播<br />\n2）聯署撐頭條新聞<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSc0nY2wXUDBKc7M9-Kza8UC5z5i698g3dc7z0782mOxJHQCUg/viewform\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSc0nY2wXUDBKc7M9-Kza8UC5z5i698g3dc7z0782mOxJHQCUg%2Fviewform&d=Vmg9VhgMmKCDk1oLDtgP7vaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=6db309ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSc0nY2wXUDBKc7M9-Kza8UC5z5i698g3dc7z0782mOxJHQCUg/viewform</a><br />\n3）寫信俾邱騰華、通訊局、港台顧委會，cc 梁家榮<br />\nDONTs<br />\n1）投訴警訊。雖然警訊係警務處嘅發聲渠道，但處理投訴嘅依然係港台。無謂令港台徒添工作喇。要投訴不如投訴TVB<br />\n<br />\n＝＝＝＝＝＝入正題＝＝＝＝＝＝<br />\n<br />\n區家麟潮池：斗膽諷刺警察，就是《頭條新聞》的原罪<br />\n<a href=\"http://aukalun.blogspot.com/2020/05/blog-post_38.html?m=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Faukalun.blogspot.com%2F2020%2F05%2Fblog-post_38.html%3Fm%3D1&d=Vmg9VhgMmKCDk1oLDtgP7vaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=7afa20d1\" target=\"_blank\">http://aukalun.blogspot.com/2020/05/blog-post_38.html?m=1</a><br />\n<br />\n區家麟講得好清晰：<br />\n//通訊局竟然認為警察屬於一種「<span style=\"color: orange;\">社會地位</span>」(social status)&nbsp;而受此條文保障，看清楚完整條文，全文如此：「持牌人不得在節目內加入&hellip;&hellip;可能導致任何人士或羣體基於民族、國籍、種族、性別、性取向、宗教、年齡、社會地位、身體或心智不健全等原因，而遭人憎恨或畏懼或受到污蔑或侮辱的材料&hellip;&hellip;」[3.2(b)]<br />\n<br />\n即是，此條文旨在保護的群體，乃有關<span style=\"color: orange;\">種族、小眾、年齡、殘障人士等身分的邊緣群體</span>，免他們受歧視，而非保護某種職業，更非保護警察//<br />\n<br />\n警察係職業，不是社會地位<br />\n警察係職業，不是社會地位<br />\n警察係職業，不是社會地位<br />\n<br />\n通訊局係over-interpret，或者監粗援引一條唔關事嘅條文嚟包庇警察。<br />\n<br />\n仲有，通訊局嘅判斷（見<a href=\"http://www.coms-auth.hk/filemanager/tc/content_713/appx_20200519.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.coms-auth.hk%2Ffilemanager%2Ftc%2Fcontent_713%2Fappx_20200519.pdf&d=Vmg9VhgMmKCDk1oLDtgP7vaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=ad2d202a\" target=\"_blank\">www.coms-auth.hk/filemanager/tc/content_713/appx_20200519.pdf</a>）：<br />\n<br />\n//一般觀眾能明顯察覺到該環節對警方作惡意的描繪，以侮辱警隊及傳達偏見，暗示警務人員均被視為廢物，遭人厭惡唾棄，也暗示只有毫無價值的人方會加入警隊，有譏笑所有服務於警隊或有志加入警隊的人之嫌//<br />\n<br />\n究竟一般觀眾係咩人？幾多人？有冇做過調查統計？如果觀眾有不正常嘅情緒反應，點解傳媒要負責？<br />\n哩個指控同教歷史卷話題目傷害國民感情一樣，即係「<span style=\"color: orange;\">你玻璃心就要我去負責</span>」。<br />\n<br />\n哩啲事只會繼續發生，仲越嚟越核突；但大家唔好慣，<br />\n<img src=\"https://mandeladayasia.files.wordpress.com/2012/07/14.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmandeladayasia.files.wordpress.com%2F2012%2F07%2F14.jpg&h=ca489c3f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"75cb9bafd6ef0fa317ba356c9db4d8dfb3a6188c","tid":2024840,"uid":184643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T01:08:26.000Z","msg":"輕輕自推"},{"pid":"b217b41e1e0e08c9c0ce3d93ae662ea2892c3d1d","tid":2024840,"uid":280475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T01:16:23.000Z","msg":"Tui"},{"pid":"7f6a96d01fde4d7a386b8abe81722c1efe3ec885","tid":2024840,"uid":184643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T01:36:15.000Z","msg":"輕輕再推"},{"pid":"ac29bdd30faf3f9e20c1ebaaeff956b64574f865","tid":2024840,"uid":297997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T01:38:04.000Z","msg":"有冇社會地位唔係班狗官自己鳩Up<br />\n<br />\n係市民認為"},{"pid":"f21b20113fde5fcedd8ae9456b4fa025702fadfd","tid":2024840,"uid":184643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac29bdd30faf3f9e20c1ebaaeff956b64574f865","tid":2024840,"uid":297997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T01:38:04.000Z","msg":"有冇社會地位唔係班狗官自己鳩Up<br />\n<br />\n係市民認為"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T01:52:33.000Z","msg":"條條例係保護社會<span style=\"color: orange;\">地位低</span>嘅人、弱勢<br />\n譬如條例之下唔可以嘲笑人拎綜援、露宿等等<br />\n<br />\n假如用哩條例嚟保護有錢人、權貴，都係荒謬嘅"},{"pid":"76c6d40afc167b0cc270045196e07866043865ad","tid":2024840,"uid":184643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T02:41:37.000Z","msg":"再三輕推"},{"pid":"d26610774f1c9a0d2265df9cc834a0b3adfb0a1e","tid":2024840,"uid":4974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T02:41:47.000Z","msg":"推 <br />\n<br />\n港台唔係condom！！"}]}